Unnamed Package

  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    arrayObject
    Class for creating objects in inventory array

    This class creates the an array and displays the items in the player's inventory.

    Commands
    Class to issue commands that interact with the pet

    This class is responsible for using commands that can interact with the pet.
    GameFile
    Class handling game data manipulation, loading, and saving

    This class is responsible for saving the game.
    ImageUtils
    Class to handle sprites and images with transparent backgrounds

    This class is responsible to accepting with transparent backgrounds and updating their colour.

    ItemArray
    Class handling array management

    Objects are added to the array and can be removed.

    ParentalControls
    Parental control functions

    This class contains all the functions for parental controls, it also displays the parental controls screen

    Pet
    Class handling pet object

    This class contains attributes for the current pet and these attributes can be updated according to the pet's state.

    PetSprite
    Class handling pet sprite images and animations

    This class opens the sprites and displays them on the screen.
    SoundPlayer
    Class that handles playing the sound

    The class accepts a filename and plays that sound file.

    TutorialScreen
    Class handling the tutorial for the game

    This class opens the tutorial screen, displays images that depict other screens in the game, and lists instructions on how to play the game.

    Windows
    Class that displays the window

    This is the main class that is responsible for displaying the main menu, displaying other screens, and creating pets.
